# API Documentation

## TCP Protocol

All communication uses JSON over TCP. Each message is prefixed with a 4-byte length field.

### Packet Structure
```json
{
  "type": "PACKET_TYPE",
  "payload": "JSON_STRING_PAYLOAD"
}
```

### Packet Types

| Type | Direction | Description |
|------|-----------|-------------|
| `AUTH_REQUEST` | Client → Server | Authentication with secret key |
| `AUTH_RESPONSE` | Server → Client | Authentication result |
| `SEND_MENU` | Client → Server | Send a dynamic menu to player |
| `MENU_RESPONSE` | Server → Client | Player's menu selection |
| `FORM_REQUEST` | Client → Server | Send a form (FormsAPI compatible) |
| `FORM_RESPONSE` | Server → Client | Player's form response |
| `PLAYER_JOIN` | Server → Client | Bedrock player joined |
| `PLAYER_LEAVE` | Server → Client | Bedrock player left |
| `PLAYER_LIST` | Client → Server | Request online player list |
| `PLAYER_LIST_RESPONSE` | Server → Client | List of online players |
| `PING` | Both | Keepalive ping |
| `PONG` | Both | Keepalive pong |
| `ERROR` | Server → Client | Error message |

---

## Authentication

Before sending any requests, you must authenticate:

### Request
```json
{
  "type": "AUTH_REQUEST",
  "payload": "{\"serverIdentifier\":\"lobby\",\"secretKey\":\"your-secret-key\"}"
}
```

### Response (Success)
```json
{
  "type": "AUTH_RESPONSE",
  "payload": "{\"success\":true,\"message\":\"Authentication successful\"}"
}
```

### Response (Failure)
```json
{
  "type": "AUTH_RESPONSE",
  "payload": "{\"success\":false,\"message\":\"Invalid secret key\"}"
}
```

---

## Sending Forms (FormsAPI Compatible)

### Simple Form (Button Menu)

```json
{
  "type": "FORM_REQUEST",
  "payload": "{\"request_id\":\"unique-id-123\",\"player_uuid\":\"00000000-0000-0000-0009-01f200e0da15\",\"form_type\":\"simple\",\"title\":\"Server Menu\",\"content\":\"Select an option:\",\"buttons\":[{\"text\":\"Teleport to Spawn\",\"command\":\"spawn\"},{\"text\":\"Open Shop\",\"image_type\":\"url\",\"image_data\":\"https://example.com/shop.png\",\"command\":\"shop\"},{\"text\":\"Player Settings\"}]}"
}
```

#### Payload Details:
```json
{
  "request_id": "unique-id-123",
  "player_uuid": "00000000-0000-0000-0009-01f200e0da15",
  "form_type": "simple",
  "title": "Server Menu",
  "content": "Select an option:",
  "buttons": [
    {
      "text": "Teleport to Spawn",
      "command": "spawn"
    },
    {
      "text": "Open Shop",
      "image_type": "url",
      "image_data": "https://example.com/shop.png",
      "command": "shop"
    },
    {
      "text": "Player Settings"
    }
  ]
}
```

#### Button Properties:
| Property | Type | Required | Description |
|----------|------|----------|-------------|
| `text` | string | Yes | Button label text |
| `command` | string | No | Command to execute when clicked (without /) |
| `image_type` | string | No | `"url"` or `"path"` for button icon |
| `image_data` | string | No | URL or resource path for the icon |

### Modal Form (Yes/No Dialog)

```json
{
  "type": "FORM_REQUEST",
  "payload": "{\"request_id\":\"unique-id-456\",\"player_uuid\":\"00000000-0000-0000-0009-01f200e0da15\",\"form_type\":\"modal\",\"title\":\"Teleport Request\",\"content\":\"PlayerA wants to teleport to you.\\n\\nDo you accept?\",\"button1\":\"Accept\",\"button2\":\"Deny\",\"command_accept\":\"tpaccept\",\"command_deny\":\"tpdeny\"}"
}
```

#### Payload Details:
```json
{
  "request_id": "unique-id-456",
  "player_uuid": "00000000-0000-0000-0009-01f200e0da15",
  "form_type": "modal",
  "title": "Teleport Request",
  "content": "PlayerA wants to teleport to you.\n\nDo you accept?",
  "button1": "Accept",
  "button2": "Deny",
  "command_accept": "tpaccept",
  "command_deny": "tpdeny"
}
```

### Form Response

When the player interacts with a form, you receive:

```json
{
  "type": "FORM_RESPONSE",
  "payload": "{\"request_id\":\"unique-id-123\",\"player_uuid\":\"00000000-0000-0000-0009-01f200e0da15\",\"response_type\":\"success\",\"clicked_button\":0,\"confirmed\":false}"
}
```

#### Response Types:
| Type | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `success` | Player clicked a button |
| `closed` | Player closed the form without selecting |
| `error` | An error occurred |

---

## Sending Dynamic Menus

For more complex menus with callback handling:

### Request
```json
{
  "type": "SEND_MENU",
  "payload": "{\"targetPlayer\":\"00000000-0000-0000-0009-01f200e0da15\",\"menuId\":\"main-menu\",\"title\":\"Server Menu\",\"content\":\"Welcome to our server!\",\"buttons\":[{\"id\":\"spawn\",\"text\":\"Teleport to Spawn\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://example.com/spawn.png\"},{\"id\":\"shop\",\"text\":\"Open Shop\"},{\"id\":\"settings\",\"text\":\"Settings\"}]}"
}
```

### Response
```json
{
  "type": "MENU_RESPONSE",
  "payload": "{\"menuId\":\"main-menu\",\"playerUuid\":\"00000000-0000-0000-0009-01f200e0da15\",\"buttonId\":\"spawn\",\"buttonIndex\":0}"
}
```

